Termubit Specification: 0071
 Title: Payment Protocol MIME Types for Termubit
 Author: AresCyu <areshin@proton.me>
 Status: Draft
 Type: Standards Track
 Created: 2026-06-18

== Abstract ==
This document defines a MIME (RFC 2046) Media Type for Termubit payment protocol message files. These types are designed to handle payment communication within the Termubit network. These MIME types are to be submitted for internal registry as our formal standards are established, following RFC 6838 section 3.2.

== Specification ==
The MIME types used for Termubit payment protocol messages are:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Message !! Type/Subtype
|-
| PaymentRequest || application/vnd.termubit.payment.request
|-
| Payment || application/vnd.termubit.payment.payment
|-
| PaymentACK || application/vnd.termubit.payment.ack
|}

